The '''''Portminian''''' was a civilian transport ship. The ship was used by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to transport [[Memah Roothes]], [[Rodo]], and several other civilian workers to the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star I]] while it was under construction at [[Despayre]].

The ship shared its name with the [[Portminia system/Legends|Portminia system]].

